0001-0001" num="0000">    <ul id="ul0002" list-style="none">        <li id="ul0002-0001" num="0000">including providing at least three portions of surface with independent and controllable vacuum means for retaining the label,</li>        <li id="ul0002-0002" num="0000">including curtailing the application of vacuum means at the first portion of the surface upon the first portion reaching the output location and</li>        <li id="ul0002-0003" num="0000">interrupting the application of vacuum means at the third portion of the surface, with the trailing edge of the label being retained at the second portion of the surface.</li>    </ul>    </li></ul></p></abstract></us-patent-application>